subsiding, given so many increasing outbreaks in other parts of the
world. It would be interesting to know what mosquito vector control
measures have been implemented in the outbreak areas. A map of
Malaysia can be accessed at:
<http://www.abcmalaysia.com/maps/wmsia_map.htm>. - Mod.TY]
